{"tid":644243,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想幫屋企隻龜間屋加過濾, 求教#adore#","createTime":"2018-04-27T06:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T11:33:21.000Z","uid":71624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"499bd2797baf87bf117365b2711fbbc0ab4ed7dc","tid":644243,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"巴西龜黎, size有成人男人兩隻手掌咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為佢大個仔, 想俾個大D嘅箱佢住, 但係要兩老日日攞個箱入洗手間換水又好辛苦, <br />\n自己都要返工唔係咁得閒日日睇住, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想set個過濾系統, <br />\n主要係要保持水質乾淨, 夠力吸走佢D屎, 因為隻龜成日痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦要過濾到佢D尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好換水果陣可以用埋個泵吸水, 方便D<br />\n<br />\n我筆直唔多, 係淘寶睇到幾個但又唔知邊種好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打都有龜, 講下可以點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b3c36d7232fa2596f07b5373b8fdd6d6830e70","tid":644243,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"上水龜論壇"},{"pid":"1f14281848359da53e9ce3e0c038c72658a5c62e","tid":644243,"uid":183930,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:33:50.000Z","msg":"如果佢已經咁大隻，你加過濾都吸吾倒d屎，只可以做到啲水有多少少氧氣，就算你加咗過濾d水都吾會清得幾多日，三之四日都系要換水。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＃自己有養"},{"pid":"3ac5bdf90dc098acbd4a28672120d70b0f19ba85","tid":644243,"uid":127007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"買支吸缷底果啲吸下屎同食物殘渣仲好<br />\n養龜幾好既過濾都係要換水"},{"pid":"c19a025aca06a5bba55e4ac904e4a3b7479232f2","tid":644243,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f14281848359da53e9ce3e0c038c72658a5c62e","tid":644243,"uid":183930,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:33:50.000Z","msg":"如果佢已經咁大隻，你加過濾都吸吾倒d屎，只可以做到啲水有多少少氧氣，就算你加咗過濾d水都吾會清得幾多日，三之四日都系要換水。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＃自己有養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好亂講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea0d4f53bf60c034ba5222e4b96803671b0a862","tid":644243,"uid":179047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"針對水龜多屎尿特性,我建議你用潛水泵加滴流盒,一層棉花加兩層生物環,我隻水魚頂到兩個星期換水"},{"pid":"4c04a4abfd26d1152fef2e3684508fcb91e59a5b","tid":644243,"uid":46674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"留名 我果隻都差唔多大"},{"pid":"b5404f7646349b4ee6963a52a6b26b530ca8ad87","tid":644243,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ea0d4f53bf60c034ba5222e4b96803671b0a862","tid":644243,"uid":179047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"針對水龜多屎尿特性,我建議你用潛水泵加滴流盒,一層棉花加兩層生物環,我隻水魚頂到兩個星期換水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:25:23.000Z","msg":"巴打潛水泵夠力吸走D屎? 我最怕唔夠力吸屎, 同埋俾D屎整壞個泵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70d3f42733e9fce9be259c4e33938a5c885075d","tid":644243,"uid":179047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"潛水泵有大有細,啲屎吸入個泵入便會攪碎啦.最重要層棉花隔走啲屎等啲生物環養到茵啲水自然會清,可以頂到兩個星期先換水"}]}